{"tid":760940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]仲有幾多人唔肯面對結婚同埋單的分別","createTime":"2018-07-30T03:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T08:40:07.000Z","uid":78016,"like":10,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84d8e01bb0ead4667e5a3a229de65a7f94e42f7b","tid":760940,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"結婚意思: 同處女或只同過新郎一人做愛的女人簽結婚證書<br />\n<br />\n埋單意思: 同非處女而且個西曾經有新郎以外的男人抽插過百幾下甚至幾千下 個西可能仲會有上一手精液的女人簽結婚證書<br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n與處女結婚的好處:<br />\n1. 研究指出 越多性伴侶的女人 越少覺得婚姻關係美滿<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://socialpathology.blogspot.com/2010/09/sexual-partner-divorce-risk.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsocialpathology.blogspot.com%2F2010%2F09%2Fsexual-partner-divorce-risk.html&d=2NJl0nWDkMNMwnfaPeqvKMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b4547eb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://socialpathology.blogspot.com/2010/09/sexual-partner-divorce-risk.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 不會與上手 上上手 上上上手 比較你的床技<br />\n<br />\n3. 無機會有 sexually transmitted disease<br />\n<br />\n4. 懷孕 唔洗驚因為落過仔 食過藥 有副作用<br />\n<br />\n5. 受教育的女人 保存個處俾老公 多數係開心 唔孤獨 家庭背景良好<br />\n<br />\n6. 個西未受其他男人抽插開發而變鬆<br />\n<br />\n7. 越多男人抽插過的女人 下一手對佢意思/意義越少<br />\n<br />\n8. 破條女處嘅男人 係永遠對佢的意義最大 你一世都改變唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b411e73555941a23c17bf623432809fa62ae188e","tid":760940,"uid":169992,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"世伯同你老母係結婚定埋單？"},{"pid":"7f33cf52597f1e6f7009dade3669db341482d448","tid":760940,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"清你信念好堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c74c6b0d21179d95036612f3099145ce6734d8","tid":760940,"uid":2263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"女人埋男人單叫唔叫埋單？"},{"pid":"dbc281c787a56cd5b30ad8616698051cd468390e","tid":760940,"uid":78016,"like":1